&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://ayoubmah.github.io/images/Pasted%20image%2020260303123027.png" alt="Pasted image 20260303123027"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="1--docker-cli"&gt;1- docker cli&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;translate commands to rest api and send it over unix socket&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker run ngnix &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; POST /container/create &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Image&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;nginx:latest&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, ....&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; sent to: /var/run/docker.sock
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;so we can talk to dockerd with it&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;like&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;curl --unix-socket /var/run/docker.sock http://localhost/containers/json
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="2--dockerd"&gt;2- dockerd&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;it&amp;rsquo;s an orchestrator&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;manage images (pull, build)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;manage volume (create net, mount)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;manage network (bridge creation, port mapping)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;docker run delegated to containerd not here&lt;/strong&gt; !!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Container Filesystem</title><link>https://ayoubmah.github.io/posts/container-filesystem/</link><pubDate>Sun, 08 Feb 2026 23:56:04 +0100</pubDate><guid>https://ayoubmah.github.io/posts/container-filesystem/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://ayoubmah.github.io/images/Pasted%20image%2020260209000710.png" alt="Pasted image 20260209000710"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://ayoubmah.github.io/images/Pasted%20image%2020260209000844.png" alt="Pasted image 20260209000844"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://ayoubmah.github.io/images/Pasted%20image%2020260209001058.png" alt="Pasted image 20260209001058"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://ayoubmah.github.io/images/Pasted%20image%2020260209001254.png" alt="Pasted image 20260209001254"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://ayoubmah.github.io/images/Pasted%20image%2020260209001457.png" alt="Pasted image 20260209001457"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Containerd under the hood</title><link>https://ayoubmah.github.io/posts/containerd-under-the-hood/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ayoubmah.github.io/posts/containerd-under-the-hood/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="phase-1-runc-raw--zero-tooling"&gt;Phase 1: runc Raw — Zero Tooling&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;so what we&amp;rsquo;ll do in this phase is exactly what containerd does internally&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;me (manually) vs containerd (automatically) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create rootfs → pulls image layers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write config.json → generates OCI bundle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Call runc run → calls runc via shim&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Watch cgroups appear → same thing happens&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;first i installed containerd
&lt;img src="https://ayoubmah.github.io/images/Pasted%20image%2020260305002032.png" alt="Pasted image 20260305002032"&gt;
so it&amp;rsquo;s automatically we can see that we have runc but not crun, (so the default OCI implementation in containerd is runc)&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>